      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BREAKOUT LAD (1) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at three of 15 starts including eight wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (25.61) over 457m at Q Lakeside. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Looks a key player drawing the cherry. HAVE IGNITION (2) finished well back at this track last time when a 2.25 lengths sixth (20.11) but scored three back at this track (20.21). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Likely to be thereabouts. CASHED UP RHI (4) goes very well this trip starting 14 times for five wins and six minors. Placed last time (20.12) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. BROOKERS ROAD (6) was well supported last time but could only manage second (19.98), beaten half a length. Overdue and gets his chance.",
